 Forbes magazine has finally confirmed Kanye West‘s billionaire status, but according to the musician, they still shorted him on his actual net-worth. Editors at the money mag claim West, 42, took issue with his published $1.3 billion estimates, texting staffers that apparently don’t know “how to count” that his net-worth… April 26, 2020 In "Entertainment" PRESIDENT of Dangote Group, Alhaji Aliko Dangote, has emerged the richest man in Africa, for the first time, with a networth of $13.8 billion, according to a report from the Forbes annual world’s billionaires ranking, released on Wednesday. March 11, 2011 In "Business" The President, Dangote Group, Alhaji Aliko Dangote, has retained Africa’s richest man title in the 2019 Forbes Africa’s Billionaires list for the eighth consecutive year, with a current net worth of $10.3 billion. January 10, 2019 In "News"